{"tid":2164853,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"奇文分享：杯葛立法會還是加入臨立會？看最反對議會的列寧和布爾什維克黨如何辦！","createTime":"2020-08-19T12:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T14:08:28.000Z","uid":276028,"like":10,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a2af742e25271798ff35ba1c425a67f9009e33f2","tid":2164853,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:18:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.boyangu.com/featured/boycott-legco-2020/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boyangu.com%2Ffeatured%2Fboycott-legco-2020%2F&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInJKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=fcf4e7f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.boyangu.com/featured/boycott-legco-2020/</a><br />\n<br />\n中共擺出分化之計，應該杯葛立法會？還是加入立法會寸土必爭？<br />\n我認為無論是杯葛立法會派還是參加立法會派，論點都是隔山打牛，無法解答我心中的疑惑：<br />\n如何在民主運動的低潮保存民主運動的火種？<br />\n不如，參考最反對資產階級議會制的列寧和布爾什維克黨如何應對沙皇的假民主選舉，了解一下前人的民主經驗，才決定杯葛立法會還是留守立法會！<br />\n<br />\n歡迎藍絲痴線佬負評文章。"},{"pid":"909f0ac960858665e78b50ab5eb9c03352c15a1b","tid":2164853,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:29:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dbaca0a276862a9356f95b688dfdf56b7d72fc2c","tid":2164853,"uid":222524,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:33:16.000Z","msg":"如果呢個係民選立法會，我會主張留<br />\n但呢個係非法委任臨立會，所以不了"},{"pid":"5b85a70a6f1bc3f5c278b7641c5debcd639cb8a4","tid":2164853,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212f0969fe5a147cb51c70b44c6a4927b12a4e38","tid":2164853,"uid":39256,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:37:15.000Z","msg":"小弟學識淺薄，真係睇唔明佢想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77887c1e543988c57ffa56a64986d07db4de0470","tid":2164853,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"dbaca0a276862a9356f95b688dfdf56b7d72fc2c","tid":2164853,"uid":222524,"like":10,"dis